{"tid":2463239,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"牆內的你們 - 陳也","createTime":"2021-03-26T14:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T14:18:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ac40ae5b3465f8d2308d0d7c81b49814664aee","tid":2463239,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210325/BN5XRBI7Z5FNZFL5VZKXLG53GM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210325%2FBN5XRBI7Z5FNZFL5VZKXLG53GM%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWnd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=e27cf015\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210325%2FBN5XRBI7Z5FNZFL5VZKXLG53GM%2F&h=4b3a4273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210325/BN5XRBI7Z5FNZFL5VZKXLG53GM/</a><br />\n<br />\n牆內的你們 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p8zdMc3GkrCG8EkOiXLXbHOlBSs=/510x332/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MF2UQZQ4X5CZXOG44DOOEVELZI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp8zdMc3GkrCG8EkOiXLXbHOlBSs%3D%2F510x332%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMF2UQZQ4X5CZXOG44DOOEVELZI.png&h=684c8772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑敖暉親筆書簡，寄語「後會有期」。<br />\n<br />\n他們說，你們每日睇報紙，汁都會撈埋。689應該很妒忌，他叻極只係數廣告，照鏡睇吓自己邊忽忠誠。<br />\n<br />\n新聞鏡頭焦點落在你們拇指食指做的心心，雙手被扣抓緊機會做出一秒的心心、豎起的手指公，雙人合力舉單臂上頭頂做出的一個心。這些，牆外人看着，雖然傷感但又覺得超合眼緣，極有生機。<br />\n<br />\n不同年齡層的香港好兒女，逆風慢行，不屈不撓，你們牆內人意外地，反過來鼓勵到牆外人。拉筋操，雞體字，一百下掌上壓，潤手霜gel頭，格仔飯，完全唔入M+流的M巾，黐出小天地的信封，與圖書館硬皮書殼，踢到識飛的毽，堅忍耐的三高，給未來孩子的缺席告假書，哼唱本土流行曲，國際化到爆燈的。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n高牆裏頭的你們，。。。。。。。。。。。，在廢物被黨操弄升級為喪屍的這個危城中，如影如水，穩步潛行。"}]}